Megatron slipped into Astroblast, and activated his 
speakers. "Decepticons" Megatrons voice boomed over the 
amplification. "We have nothing to gain now, withdraw. Shockwave, I 
know this may be hard for you to believe but it is me, meet me at 
these coordinates, away from base. We will talk. The rest of you 
return to base, and begin repairs." He finished.
